channel.title: Zeph AMA (ask me anything) and discussion
channel.description:
What do you guys honestly think about my stuff. I would like to know what the community thinks of me.
Anything from my most recent song to my oldest, my personality, reputation, things I need to work on etc. is up for discussion.
An AMA (ask me anything) is also possible.
P.S. Negative comments welcome.

item.title: Zeph AMA (ask me anything) and discussion
item.dc:creator: Zeph
item.description:
Just keep persevering bro, there’s no secret to it. Practice makes perfect I still don’t consider myself that great, but thank you for the compliment
